Maxima Set Megatron's fusion cannon back next to him. Then made her way to 
the door, leaving the bridge as she neared the newcomers. 

She was in transmetal body for this era. A mix of a white tiger & a hawk. But 
her glowing crimson optics stayed the same as she neared Scourge & the 
others. Her gaze just as piercing & wicked as it ever was. "So.. you claim to 
have been from Megatron. Then if so.. you know who I am," she stepped up to 
Scourge. 

--part1_1cc.9c0906f.2bf8655b_boundary
